TRAGEDY ON THE CHANNEL
Seven passengers escape.

762
01:34:00,075 --> 01:34:02,995
Very bad weather
on the English Channel

763
01:34:03,204 --> 01:34:06,248
is making the rescuers' task
all the more difficult.

764
01:34:06,457 --> 01:34:08,876
Several fishermen
are reported missing

765
01:34:09,085 --> 01:34:12,297
as are two people
