766
01:34:12,631 --> 01:34:15,133
The cause of the accident
is unknown.

767
01:34:15,342 --> 01:34:16,718
According to sources,

768
01:34:16,927 --> 01:34:19,972
the ferry was carrying
1435 passengers.

769
01:34:20,389 --> 01:34:22,767
Rescue operations
are still under way.

770
01:34:22,975 --> 01:34:25,478
Hundreds of bodies
have been recovered.

771
01:34:25,686 --> 01:34:28,649
Many passengers are still missing.

772
01:34:32,319 --> 01:34:35,573
A police boat,
responding to the SOS,

773
01:34:36,074 --> 01:34:39,410
retrieved 7 passengers.
