774
01:34:52,467 --> 01:34:56,846
The widow of a French composer
who died last year, Julie Vignon.

775
01:34:58,682 --> 01:35:01,936
Steven Killian, English citizen,
barman on the ferry.

776
01:35:02,478 --> 01:35:03,187
A businessman

777
01:35:03,437 --> 01:35:05,314
from Poland, Karol Karol.

778
01:35:06,983 --> 01:35:09,528
