779
01:35:12,864 --> 01:35:14,992
Frenchman Oliver Benoit.

780
01:35:21,332 --> 01:35:24,585
Among the survivors
are also two Swiss citizens:

781
01:35:34,931 --> 01:35:37,475
Auguste Bruner, judge,

782
01:35:43,607 --> 01:35:46,735
and a model, student
at the University of Geneva,

